casebody.data:
ELLIOTT HOMES
v.
S.C. (HICKS) S239804 Supreme Court of California March 15, 2017

*717Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Werdegar, Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

Review granted on the court's own motion; briefing deferred

Review is ordered on the court's own motion. Further action in this matter is deferred pending consideration and disposition of a related issue in McMillin Albany v. Superior Court, S229762 (See Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.512(d)(2) ), or pending further order of the court. Submission of additional briefing, pursuant to California Rules of Court, rule 8.520, is deferred pending further order of the court.
